{'id': 36209030, 'body': 'HI there! To discontinue the 3rd-party affirmations, you can delete your name from the app. Also, the affirmations you "like" (if you hit the heart icon) are saved to your Favorites, so you can view them at any time you'd like or set up them as your widget, notification, etc. 

We're always looking for ways to improve our app, so we appreciate your suggestions. We'll pass them along to our development team.
